	<text>
		<body>
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_002392_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1'-->
<!--hand 01 56 top left-->
<lb/><p><space extent="3" unit="chars"/>50 Albermarle <choice><abbr>St</abbr><expan>Street</expan></choice></p>
<lb/><p><space extent="1" unit="words"/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>London </p>
<lb/><p rend="right">11 <choice><abbr>Aug</abbr><expan>August</expan></choice>1865 </p>
<lb/><p>Dear Sir </p>
<lb/><p><space extent="1" unit="words"/><space extent="1" unit="chars"/>I regret that 
<lb/>I am unable to afford 
<lb/>you any information 
<lb/>about such a 
<lb/>situation as you 
<lb/>require. I am 
<lb/>not taking out 
<lb/>an expedition of 
<lb/>Europeans &amp; 
<lb/>cannot therefore 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_002392_0002"/><!--pb/@n='2'-->
<lb/>offer you any hopes 
<lb/>in it. Liverpool 
<lb/>would perhaps be 
<lb/>the place where 
<lb/>such appointments 
<lb/>as you wish may 
<lb/>be found. Wishing 
<lb/>you better success 
<lb/>there</p>
<lb/><p>I am &amp; </p>
<lb/><p rend="no-indent">David Livingstone </p><!--hand 02 11 Aug. 1865. bottom left--><!-- hand 03 A.167 bottom right-->
			
</div>
